comment: This was an amazing experience! I learned so much about AI and got to work with a fantastic team. The mentorship was top-notch.
Great course with very detailed explanations. Some of the later videos could have been a bit more concise, but overall I learned a lot.
Perfect introduction to Python for data science. The instructor made complex topics easy to understand. Highly recommend!
The work was interesting, but I felt a bit isolated from the main team since it was a remote position. More structured team-building activities would have been nice.
